Package com.frijolie.cards

Class PlayingCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.frijolie.cards.PlayingCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Card, java.lang.Comparable<Card>
    public class PlayingCard
extends java.lang.Object
implements Card
    A concrete class used to implement behavior of a playing card. Implements the interface Card.

    This object assumes that each card has a Rank, Suit, and value.

    Since:
    0.1

      • hashCode

        public int hashCode()
        A method to generate a unique integer value for every card.

        A salt value is added to the ordinal values of Rank and Suit. This value is then multiplied by another salt value to generate the hashcode of a card.

        Specified by:
